Description Title: The web page will have the title "Trillium Media Design,"
which appears in the browser tab. Header: At the top of the page, there will be
a header section containing the main heading "Trillium Media Design." This text
will be displayed in a large font and will be styled with a white background and
blue text, making it stand out against the dark background of the body.
Navigation Bar: Below the header, there will be a simple navigation bar that
includes links to "Home," "About," and "Services." These links will be styled
with the same blue color as the header, making them easy to read against the
background. Body Text: The main content area will feature a paragraph describing
the services provided by Trillium Media Design. This text will be in a light
gray color, making it readable against the dark blue background. The font will
be Arial or another sans-serif typeface, ensuring a modern and clean look.
Footer: At the bottom of the page, there will be a footer with a copyright
notice, displayed in italicized and smaller text, indicating the year and the
name of the company.
